Object surface (the tiles)
Always affects only that oscillator

Parameter panel
Affects all selected oscillators

This gives you:

Interaction	Scope
Click waveform	That oscillator
Toggle waveform	That oscillator
Change waveform type (panel)	All selected
Change rate (panel)	All selected
This creates a very stable mental model:

"Things I touch directly act locally."
"Things in the inspector act globally."

Users learn this extremely fast.

